## 1. Project Overview

This is a personal professional landing page for Drew Peterson, a dual B.B.A. candidate in Finance and Business Analytics & Information Systems at the University of Iowa (graduating December 2026). The site is designed for recruiters and hiring managers at commercial real estate firms in the Midwest who want to quickly assess Drew's internship experience and analytical skills. Success means the page is live, publicly accessible, and shared with at least 5 target CRE employers as part of job applications within 30–60 days of launch.

